        {
            "id": "821791621",
            "title": "周四热门中概涨跌不一，网易涨0.12%，台积电跌1.57%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article\" id=\"artibody\">\n<!-- 相关专题top start-->\n<!-- 相关专题top end-->\n<!-- 期货推广begin -->\n<!-- 期货推广end -->\n<!-- 秒拍begin -->\n<!-- 秒拍end -->\n<!-- 视频播放器start -->\n<!-- 视频播放器end -->\n<!-- 行情图begin -->\n<!-- 行情图end -->\n<p>　　周四热门中概涨跌不一，<span id=\"usstock_.IXIC\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/.IXIC.html\" target=\"_blank\">纳斯达克</a></span><span id=\"quote_.IXIC\"></span>中国金龙指数（HXC）收跌0.91%。</p>\n<p>　　上涨股当中（按市值从高到低），<span id=\"usstock_NTES\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/NTES.html\" target=\"_blank\">网易</a></span><span id=\"quote_NTES\"></span>涨0.12%，携程涨0.54%，<span id=\"usstock_CHT\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/CHT.html\" target=\"_blank\">中华电信</a></span><span id=\"quote_CHT\"></span>涨0.21%，<span id=\"usstock_ASX\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/ASX.html\" target=\"_blank\">日月光半导体</a></span><span id=\"quote_ASX\"></span>涨5.41%，<span id=\"usstock_UMC\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/UMC.html\" target=\"_blank\">联电</a></span><span id=\"quote_UMC\"></span>涨0.07%，<span id=\"usstock_NIO\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/NIO.html\" target=\"_blank\">蔚来</a></span><span id=\"quote_NIO\"></span>涨0.44%，满帮涨1.08%，中国新城农村涨1.46%，<span id=\"usstock_HTHT\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/HTHT.html\" target=\"_blank\">华住酒店集团</a></span><span id=\"quote_HTHT\"></span>涨0.54%，<span id=\"usstock_BILI\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BILI.html\" target=\"_blank\">哔哩哔哩</a></span><span id=\"quote_BILI\"></span>涨1.53%，<span id=\"usstock_VIPS\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/VIPS.html\" target=\"_blank\">唯品会</a></span><span id=\"quote_VIPS\"></span>涨0.72%，<span id=\"usstock_ZK\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/ZK.html\" target=\"_blank\">极氪</a></span><span id=\"quote_ZK\"></span>涨1.03%。</p>\n<p>　　下跌股当中（按市值从高到低），<span id=\"usstock_TSM\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/TSM.html\" target=\"_blank\">台积电</a></span><span id=\"quote_TSM\"></span>跌1.57%，<span id=\"usstock_BABA\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BABA.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span id=\"usstock_BABA\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BABA.html\" target=\"_blank\">阿里</a></span><span id=\"quote_BABA\"></span>巴巴</a></span><span id=\"quote_BABA\"></span>跌0.51%，<span id=\"usstock_PDD\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/PDD.html\" target=\"_blank\">拼多多</a></span><span id=\"quote_PDD\"></span>跌0.18%，<span id=\"usstock_JD\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/JD.html\" target=\"_blank\">京东</a></span><span id=\"quote_JD\"></span>跌1.21%，<span id=\"usstock_BIDU\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BIDU.html\" target=\"_blank\">百度</a></span><span id=\"quote_BIDU\"></span>跌0.57%，<span id=\"usstock_TME\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/TME.html\" target=\"_blank\">腾讯音乐</a></span><span id=\"quote_TME\"></span>跌1.37%，<span id=\"usstock_LI\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/LI.html\" target=\"_blank\">理想</a></span><span id=\"quote_LI\"></span>汽车跌0.66%，<span id=\"usstock_FUTU\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/FUTU.html\" target=\"_blank\">富途</a></span><span id=\"quote_FUTU\"></span>控股跌0.50%，<span id=\"usstock_BEKE\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BEKE.html\" target=\"_blank\">贝壳</a></span><span id=\"quote_BEKE\"></span>跌0.25%，小鹏汽车跌1.22%，<span id=\"usstock_ZTO\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/ZTO.html\" target=\"_blank\">中通</a></span><span id=\"quote_ZTO\"></span>跌0.05%，BOSS直聘跌2.27%，<span id=\"usstock_EDU\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/EDU.html\" target=\"_blank\">新东方</a></span><span id=\"quote_EDU\"></span>跌5.20%，小马智行跌3.75%，名创优品跌1.80%，万国数据跌1.71%。</p>\n<p>　　美股周四收跌。对银行业坏账的担忧使银行股普跌，令三大股指早盘涨幅荡然无存。交易员同时还面临持续贸易紧张局势及美国政府停摆的双重压力。</p>\n<p>　　道指跌301.07点，跌幅为0.65%，报45952.24点；纳指跌107.54点，跌幅为0.47%，报22562.54点；标普500指数跌41.99点，跌幅为0.63%，报6629.07点。</p>\n<p>　　领涨中概股列表：</p>\n<div class=\"img_wrapper\"><img alt=\"\" data-link=\"\" src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/transform/618/w550h1668/20251017/6708-885065ebba09a6f2867738d2f682adc1.png\"/><span class=\"img_descr\"></span></div>\n<p>　　领跌中概股列表：</p>\n<div class=\"img_wrapper\"><img alt=\"\" data-link=\"\" src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/transform/346/w550h4596/20251017/6ae3-7ae1137c0901a41e67e560c47673d1fb.png\"/><span class=\"img_descr\"></span></div>\n<p>　　<a data-comos-dataid=\"wpcomos:148309\" href=\"http://finance.sina.cn/app/auto_download_finapp.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">（截图来自新浪财经APP 行情-美股-中概股热门板块）下载新浪财经APP</a></p><!-- news_keyword_pub,usstock,NTES&BIDU&EDU&.IXIC&ASX&TSM&UMC&HTHT&CHT&VIPS&JD&BABA&BABA&ZTO&BILI&PDD&NIO&TME&FUTU&LI&BEKE&ZK -->\n<!-- 正文下iframe -->\n<!-- 正文下iframe -->\n<!-- 总声明-->\n<!-- 总声明-->\n<!-- 文末二维码 start -->\n<!-- 文末二维码 start -->\n\n\n<!-- 文末二维码 start -->\n<!-- 文末二维码 start -->\n<!-- 编辑姓名及工作代码 -->\n\n<!-- 编辑姓名及工作代码-->\n</div>",
